name: Breathing Additive Geometry
description:
One of the latest 2016 trapcode TAO experiments. [28-11-16] 3 days before my mother passed away by appointed assisted death after battling with cancer with great dignity during 5 years. On the 22th anniversary of my father's passing. When I made this, it was not a particular good period of my life. I was trying to breathe my anxieties away and discover new ways to find simpler meaning and beauty in existence by delving into geometry and color. 
1:1 | 1080x1080 | 24 fps | 81fames
